News
Security
------
A vehicle of the response was slightly damaged, and 3 policemen were slightly injured after a stone attack of a convoy of a dignified and secure burial team (EDS) that occurred at the Kanzunza cemetery in Butembo town on Sun 19 May 2019. In recent times, people living near certain public cemeteries are hostile to the EDS teams that are burying those who died of Ebola. The urban authorities and the coordination of the response organized a meeting on this subject on Mon 20 May 2019.

